How did you find it? :)


> Since callers aren't
> +	 * aware of the reference count change, call pci_dev_put() now to
> +	 * avoid leaks.
> +	 */
> +	if (pdev)
> +		pci_dev_put(pdev);
> +
> +	return pdev;
>  }
>  
>  /* Given a NPU device get the associated PCI device. */
